# استقرار پلتفرم (Pelak)

تنها deploy: `apps/pelak` — جزئیات: `docs/DEPLOYMENT.md`

## جداسازی مراحل

| مرحله | زمان | دستور |
|-------|------|--------|
| Build image | CI / docker build | `npm run build -w @nextgen-cms/pelak` |
| Migrate | هر startup | `npm run db:migrate` |
| Seed | first-boot | `FIRST_BOOT=1 npm run db:seed` |
| Backup | قبل migrate prod | `docker/docker-entrypoint.sh` |

**هرگز** migrate/seed در `build`.

## Docker

- `docker/Dockerfile` — multi-stage standalone
- Entrypoint: `docker/docker-entrypoint.sh`
- Server: `node apps/pelak/server.js`
- Volume: `/data` · Health: `GET /api/health`

## توسعه محلی

```bash
npm run db:setup && npm run dev
```
